<div class="definition" id="definition-ILT" acro="ILT" titletext="Injective Linear Transformation">
<h5 class="definition">
<span class="type">Definition </span><span class="acro">ILT</span> <span class="titletext"> Injective Linear Transformation</span>
</h5>
<p>Suppose $\ltdefn{T}{U}{V}$ is a linear transformation.  Then $T$ is <em class="term">injective</em> if whenever $\lt{T}{\vect{x}}=\lt{T}{\vect{y}}$, then $\vect{x}=\vect{y}$.</p>
